    "description": "DOCUMENTATION: A flaw was found in Exiv2. Improper input validation of the rawData.size property in the Jp2Image::readMetadata() function in jp2image.cpp can lead to a heap-based buffer overflow via a crafted JPG image containing malicious EXIF data. The highest threat from this vulnerability is to confidentiality and system availability.",
